des:
Addlon products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your smart device.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your smart device - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your smart device products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Addlon" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Addlon" app;
(3). You need to have some Addlon devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Addlon" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Addlon Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Addlon Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Addlon Smart", and you'll be navigated to "Addlon Smart" login page;
(9). Input your Addlon account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
